dct_title_s: Map of Elizabeth Town, N.J. at the tome of the Revolutionary War, 1775-1783 [copy 2]
dct_description_sm: Cadastral map showing land ownership. Shows "The fortifications and positions of the British forces from June 8th to June 23d, 1780 ..." Includes index to "Names of owners referred to by number" and "References and historical notes."
